《'''玩酷人生'''》（{{lang-en|''Viva la Vida or Death and All His Friends''}}，通常简称为{{Lang|en|''Viva la Vida''}}）是英国[[摇滚乐|摇滚]]组合[[酷玩乐队|酷玩乐队]]的第四张录音室专辑，由[[Parlophone|Parlophone]]发行于2008年6月12日。專輯的名稱来源[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]中的一句短语，意思是“活在当下”、“生活万岁”。从歌词上来看，这张专辑表达的主题包含了爱、生活、死亡与战争。

专辑录制于2007年6月到2008年4月期间，{{le|乔恩·霍普金斯|Jon Hopkins}}、{{Le|里克·辛普森|Rik Simpson}}、{{Le|马库斯·德拉夫斯|Markus Dravs}}和[[布莱恩·伊诺|布莱恩·伊诺]]参与了专辑的制作。这张专辑是伊诺第一次制作的酷玩乐队的专辑，也是长久以来{{Le|肯·尼尔森|Ken Nelson}}第一次没有参与酷玩乐队专辑制作的专辑。因为伊诺要求专辑中的每首歌曲听起来都要有不一样的感觉，乐队便强迫自己去探索新的风格，所以该专辑的发行日期也就一次次地推迟了。专辑的封面是[[欧仁·德拉克罗瓦|欧仁·德拉克罗瓦]]创作的描绘[[法国七月革命|法国七月革命]]的《[[自由引导人民|自由引导人民]]》。

《玩酷人生》是一张乐评和商业成绩都很成功的专辑。专辑中有五首歌曲作为商业单曲发行：《{{le|紫罗兰盛放的山丘|Violet Hill (song)}}》和《[[生命万岁|-{zh-cn:生命万岁; zh-tw:玩酷人生}-]]》发行于2008年5月；《{{le|日本恋人|Lovers in Japan}}》和《{{le|迷失！|Lost!}}》发行于2008年11月；《{{le|草莓秋千|Strawberry Swing}}》发行于2009年11月。《-{zh-cn:生命万岁; zh-tw:玩酷人生}-》成为了乐队第一支登顶英美两国单曲榜的歌曲。专辑在[[第51届格莱美奖|2009年格莱美奖]]上获得了“[[格莱美奖最佳摇滚专辑|最佳摇滚专辑]]”奖项以及“{{Le|格莱美奖年度专辑|Grammy_Award_for_Album_of_the_Year|年度专辑}}”的提名，并成为了2008年销量最高的专辑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/top50-2008.pdf |title=IFPI Top 50 Global Best Selling Albums for 2008 |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=31 December 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090324201403/http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/top50-2008.pdf |archivedate=24 March 2009}}</ref>。截至2011年，专辑销量已超过1,000万<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.ie/music/news/a347403/coldplays-mylo-xyloto-to-beat-adeles-21-in-first-week-sales.html |title=Coldplay's 'Mylo Xyloto' to beat Adele's '21' in first-week sales? - Music News - Digital Spy |publisher=Digitalspy.ie |date=2011-10-25 |accessdate=2012-12-19 |archive-date=2012-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120712212508/http://www.digitalspy.ie/music/news/a347403/coldplays-mylo-xyloto-to-beat-adeles-21-in-first-week-sales.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年11月25日，《玩酷人生》发行了包含[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]《[[进行曲_(酷玩乐团)|进行曲]]》的豪华版，其中包含了另一首热单《{{le|再续鲜艳人生|Life in Technicolor II}}》。

== 製作 ==
[[氛圍音樂|氛圍音樂]]家和英國唱片製作人[[布萊恩·伊諾|布萊恩·伊諾]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003538468|title=Coldplay drafts Eno to produce fourth album|author=Cohen, Jonathon|publisher=''[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]''|date=26 January 2007|accessdate=18 August 2008|archive-date=2012-05-26|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120526023650/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003538468%23/bbcom/search/google/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003538468|dead-url=no}}</ref> 參與了這張專輯的製作。酷玩樂隊在結束了他們的拉美巡迴演唱會之後，搬到了一個叫做The Bakery的地方並在那裡建了一個錄音棚。他們在那裡製作歌曲。酷玩樂隊在網站上對歌迷公開了專輯的製作。

== 反響 ==
=== 銷量 ===
[[File:Coldplay_Viva_La_Vida_Tour_in_Hannover_August_25th_2009.jpg|thumb]]]]
專輯在全世界都取得了很好的銷量。發行之後的首個禮拜就在世界上36個國家獲得第一<ref>[http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1034807&c=3 Viva La Vida scales global chart heights] {{Wayback|url=http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1034807&c=3 |date=20141205072255 }} Music Week, Retrieved 11 July 2008</ref> 在英國，專輯上市首日就銷售出125,000張，發行後三日內銷量達到302,074張，發行就登上排行首位。<ref name="uk chart">{{cite web|first=Paul|last=Sexton|url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003816825|title=New Coldplay Album Sells 300K In Three Days|accessdate=10 July 2008|date=16 June 2008|publisher=Billboard|archive-date=2012-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110104126/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003816825|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在其上市後第二個禮拜又銷售198,000張，達到白金認證。<ref name=mw1034631/> 專輯發行後10天內銷量達到500,000張，超過了酷玩第3張X&Y專輯在英國的銷量<ref name=mw1034631>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1034631&c=1|title=Coldplay album breaks through 500,000 UK sales in 10 days|accessdate=23 June 2008|publisher=[[Music_Week|Music Week]]|archive-date=2012-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212124213/http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1034631&c=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美國，其上市首日銷量達到316,000張，發行後首個禮拜銷量達720,000張<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emigroup.com/Press/2008/press75.htm|title=Coldplay’s Viva La Vida simultaneously tops the US and UK album charts|accessdate=17 August 2008|date=25 June 2008|publisher=EMI|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080802040810/http://www.emigroup.com/Press/2008/press75.htm|archivedate=2008年8月2日|deadurl=yes}}</ref> 並在排行榜上連續兩個禮拜排名首位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003817876|title=Coldplay Headed To No. 1 On Billboard 200, Hot 100|authors=Caulfield, Keith; Pietroluongo, Silvio|accessdate=17 August 2008|date=18 June 2008|publisher=''[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]''|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629213447/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003817876|dead-url=no}}</ref> Viva la Vida也獲得了[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]的銷量雙白金認證。<ref name="riaa">{{Cite news|url=http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?id=8D0F0B14-C635-C0C4-3BB3-AA7B45F4D0BE|title=Viva La Coldplay|date=24 November 2008|publisher=Recording Industry Association of America|accessdate=25 December 2008|archive-date=2008-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216155923/http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?id=8D0F0B14-C635-C0C4-3BB3-AA7B45F4D0BE|dead-url=no}}</ref> Viva la Vida是有史以來被收費下載次數最多的專輯，被下載超過702,000次。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart_watch/33507/week-ending-april-26-2009-3-million-downloads-in-record-time/|title=Week Ending April 26, 2009: 3 Million Downloads In Record Time|accessdate=29 April 2009|date=29 April 2009|publisher=Yahoo|archive-date=2012-04-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66uXYeKPW?url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-april-26-2009-3-million-downloads-in-record-time.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart_watch/9716/week-ending-june-29-2008-viva-la-download-or-death-and-all-his-cds|title=Week Ending 29 June 2008: Viva la Download or Death And All His CDs|accessdate=10 July 2008|date=29 June 2008|publisher=Yahoo|archive-date=2008-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080715103245/http://new.music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart_watch/9716/week-ending-june-29-2008-viva-la-download-or-death-and-all-his-cds|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1600476/20081202/brown__chris__18_.jhtml|title=Chris Brown, Britney Spears, Coldplay, Leona Lewis And Alicia Keys Are All #1 In 2008|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=2 December 2008|publisher=MTV|accessdate=3 December 2008|archive-date=2009-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028130636/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1600476/20081202/brown__chris__18_.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 至2008年底，Viva la Vida在美國銷售超2,144,000張，是美國第二暢銷的專輯。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/lil-wayne-notches-top-selling-album-of-08-1003926030.story|title=Lil Wayne Notches Top-Selling Album Of '08|last=Cohen|first=Jonathan|date=31 December 2008|work=Billboard|publisher=Nielsen Business Media, Inc|accessdate=23 March 2009|archive-date=2011-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128184546/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/lil-wayne-notches-top-selling-album-of-08-1003926030.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marketwatch.com/news/story/2008-us-music-purchases-exceed/story.aspx?guid={6335B083-3284-461F-A0C7-C018F0997DBA}&dist=msr_3|title=2008 U.S. Music Purchases Exceed 1.5 Billion; Growth in Overall Music Purchases Exceeds 10%|accessdate=1 January 2009|date=31 December 2008|publisher=MarketWatch}}</ref> 截止到2011年8月，這張專輯在美國銷售超過280萬張<ref>{{cite web|last=Waddell|first=Ray|title=Coldplay: The Billboard Cover Story|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/features/coldplay-the-billboard-cover-story-1005314152.story|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=12 August 2011|date=12 August 2011|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120728/http://www.billboard.com/%23/artist/eddie-murphy/chart-history/1173?f=305&g=Albums#/features/coldplay-the-billboard-cover-story-1005314152.story|dead-url=no}}</ref> 就全球來看，這張專輯也是2008年全球最暢銷的專輯。<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 50 Global Best Selling Albums for 2008|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/top50-2008.pdf|publisher=[[International_Federation_of_the_Phonographic_Industry|International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=8 June 2010|archive-date=2009-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090324201403/http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/top50-2008.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 評價 ===
這張專輯於獲得了[[第51届格莱美奖|2009年格萊美獎]]最佳搖滾專輯獎的獎項<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1604545/20090208/story.jhtml|title=Grammy 2009 Winners List|author=MTV News Staff|date=8 February 2009|publisher=MTV|accessdate=9 February 2009|archive-date=2010-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101001031948/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1604545/20090208/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯被一些報刊評為2008年最佳專輯，如紐約郵報（第1）<ref>[http://www.nypost.com/seven/12072008/entertainment/music/best_of_2008_142978.htm?page=0 BEST OF 2008 CHRIS MARTIN & CO ROCK THEIR WAY TO THE TOP OF THIS YEAR'S BEST ALBUMS] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120913024547/http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/music/item_62w2Ea9QDsJpG6eAIAqbjP;jsessionid=77BD5D447C3442BA1F6CF81D0A62DFFD |date=2012-09-13 }} NYPOST.com, 7 December 2008</ref>；滾石雜誌（第7）<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted 25 Dec 2008 7:30 PM |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/24958695/albums_of_the_year/11 |title=The 50 Best Albums of 2008 |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=25 December 2008 |accessdate=2009-12-31 |archive-date=2009-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505231817/http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/24958695/albums_of_the_year/11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；Q（第3）<ref>"[http://www.qthemusic.com/cgi-bin/50bestalbums/month.pl The 50 Best Albums] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223113329/http://www.qthemusic.com/cgi-bin/50bestalbums/month.pl |date=2009-02-23 }}" ''[[Q_Magazine|Q Magazine]]'' (January 2009) p. 87, Retrieved on 29 January 2009</ref>；Spin雜誌（第9）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spin.com/articles/40-best-albums-2008?page=0,3 |title=The 40 Best Albums of 2008 | Spin Magazine Online |publisher=Spin.com |date= |accessdate=2009-12-31 |archive-date=2008-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081214001429/http://www.spin.com/articles/40-best-albums-2008?page=0%2C3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 雖然有很多人對專輯好評，不過[[NME|NME]]雜誌在[[新音樂快遞音樂獎|NME獎]]中將這張專輯提名為2009年最差專輯<ref>[http://www.nme.com/news/shockwaves-nme-awards-2008-big-gig/42311 Oasis, Alex Turner, Killers: Shockwaves NME Awards 2009 nominations] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nme.com/news/shockwaves-nme-awards-2008-big-gig/42311 |date=20110805011723 }} NME.com, 26 January 2009</ref> 。

